## Copilot Skills

The following step-by-step skills are available (shipped with genai-tk) for common extension tasks:

| Skill | Description |
|-------|-------------|
| `add-cli-command` | Create a new CLI command group and register it |
| `add-webapp-page` | Create a new Streamlit page and register it |
| `add-agent-profile` | Configure a new agent profile with tools |
| `add-chain` | Create a new LCEL chain and register it |

These are located in the genai-tk package under `skills/copilot/`.
